Definition: diffusing warmth and friendliness
Example: an affable smile; an amiable gathering; cordial relations; a cordial greeting; a genial host
Synonyms: noun, attribute, affability, affableness, amiable, feeling, amiability, state, amity, cordial, cordiality, genial, geniality, diffusing, warmth, and, friendliness, an, smile, gathering, relations, a, greeting, host
Category: adj.all
